arts.ttl: Alonso Martínez, Matt Freese lead NYCFC to 1-0 victory over Union
arts.sum: Alonso Martínez scored early in the second half for New York City FC and Matt Freese made it stand up for a 1-0 victory over Philadelphia at Citi Field on Saturday night in the Union’s first match without Dániel Gazdag. Freese finished with two saves on the way to his second shutout in eight starts this season for NYCFC.
